    "content": "Tuning: EADG\r\n\r\n[tab][Main riff] (x2)\r\nG|--------------------|\r\nD|--------------------|\r\nA|-5-4----------------|\r\nE|-----3-5-(5)-(5)(5)-| (x4)[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|--------------------|\r\nD|--------------------|\r\nA|------2---------2---|\r\nE|-0-h3---3--0-h3---3-| [/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|------|\r\nD|------|\r\nA|-17\\5-|\r\nE|------| [/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab](A)\r\nG|------------------------------------|\r\nD|----12---------------12----1514-----|\r\nA|-------12--141514-------12----------|\r\nE|-10---------------10----------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab](B)                         1  2  1\r\nG|--------------------------------------| (The bit in [] is played really fast.\r\nD|----12-------------------[------12]---| the 1 2 1 above it is your fingers\r\nA|-------12--141514--------[10-12---]---| to use (index is 1, middle is 2)\r\nE|-10---------------10-10---------------| for all you players like me who\r\n                                        use fingers.  Also I bar the 12 to\r\n                                        hit both the notes without having\r\n                                        awkward hand positions.)[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab](A)\r\nG|------------------------------------|\r\nD|----12---------------12----1514-----|\r\nA|-------12--141514-------12----------|\r\nE|-10---------------10----------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab](C)\r\nG|---------------------------------------|\r\nD|----12---------------12-------------12-|\r\nA|-------12--141514-------12----10-12----|\r\nE|-10---------------10-------10----------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n************************************\r\n\r\n| (n)  Ghost note\r\n| h    Hammer-on\r\n| \\    Slide down\r\n\r\n************************************",
